## API Reference

All protected routes require:
```
Authorization: Bearer <token>
```

---

### Auth  `/api/auth`

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/register` | Public | Register student or supervisor |
| POST | `/login` | Public | Login and receive JWT |
| GET | `/me` | Private | Get current user profile |
| PUT | `/update-password` | Private | Change password |

**Register body:**
```json
{
  "name": "Allan Mukasa",
  "email": "allan@students.cavendish.ac.ug",
  "password": "securepass",
  "role": "student",
  "studentId": "CU2021/BSC/001",
  "course": "BSc Computer Science",
  "yearOfStudy": 3
}
```
For supervisor, use `"role": "supervisor"` and include `organization`, `jobTitle`, `phone`.

---

### Internships  `/api/internships`

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/` | Public | List open internships (filter: `status`, `type`, `search`, `page`, `limit`) |
| GET | `/:id` | Public | Get single internship details |
| GET | `/my` | Supervisor | Get own internship listings |
| POST | `/` | Supervisor | Create new internship |
| PUT | `/:id` | Supervisor/Admin | Update internship |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Supervisor/Admin | Delete internship |

**Create internship body:**
```json
{
  "title": "Software Engineering Intern",
  "description": "...",
  "company": "TechCorp Uganda",
  "location": "Kampala",
  "type": "hybrid",
  "duration": "3 months",
  "applicationDeadline": "2025-05-15",
  "slots": 3,
  "skills": ["JavaScript", "React"],
  "stipend": "UGX 300,000/month"
}
```

---

### Applications  `/api/applications`

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/` | Student | Apply for internship (multipart/form-data with optional `resume` file) |
| GET | `/my` | Student | Get own applications |
| GET | `/my-interns` | Supervisor | Get all accepted interns across own internships |
| GET | `/internship/:id` | Supervisor/Admin | Get all applicants for an internship |
| PUT | `/:id/review` | Supervisor | Accept / reject / mark reviewing |
| PUT | `/:id/withdraw` | Student | Withdraw a pending application |

**Apply body (multipart/form-data):**
```
internshipId: <id>
coverLetter: "I am very interested..."
resume: <file> (optional, PDF/DOC/image, max 5MB)
```

**Review body:**
```json
{
  "status": "accepted",
  "supervisorNote": "Strong candidate, looking forward to working with you.",
  "startDate": "2025-06-01",
  "endDate": "2025-08-31"
}
```

---

### Reports  `/api/reports`

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/` | Student/Supervisor | Submit weekly report (multipart/form-data) |
| GET | `/my` | Student/Supervisor | Get own submitted reports |
| GET | `/supervisor-overview` | Supervisor | All reports for supervisor's internships |
| GET | `/application/:id` | Student/Supervisor/Admin | Get all reports for an application (grouped by week) |
| PUT | `/:id` | Report author | Edit own report |

**Submit report body (multipart/form-data):**
```
applicationId: <id>
weekNumber: 1
title: "Week 1 Progress Report"
activitiesCarriedOut: "..."   (student)
skillsLearned: "..."          (student)
challenges: "..."             (student)
goalsForNextWeek: "..."       (student)
studentPerformance: "..."     (supervisor)
areasOfImprovement: "..."     (supervisor)
overallFeedback: "..."        (supervisor)
rating: 4                     (supervisor, 1-5)
attachments: <files>          (up to 5 files)
```

---

### Admin  `/api/admin`  *(Admin only)*

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/stats` | Platform-wide statistics |
| GET | `/users` | All users (filter: `role`, `isApproved`, `search`, `page`) |
| PUT | `/users/:id/approve` | Approve or revoke a supervisor |
| PUT | `/users/:id` | Update any user |
| DELETE | `/users/:id` | Delete a user |
| GET | `/internships` | All internships regardless of status |
| GET | `/applications` | All applications (filter: `status`) |
| GET | `/reports` | All submitted reports |

---

### Users  `/api/users`

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| PUT | `/profile` | Private | Update own profile (multipart/form-data with optional `profilePhoto`) |
| GET | `/:id` | Private | Get any user's profile |

