## Roles & Permissions Summary

| Action | Student | Supervisor | Admin |
|---|---|---|---|
| Browse internships | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Apply for internship | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Create internship | ❌ | ✅ (if approved) | ❌ |
| Review applications | ❌ | ✅ (own) | ✅ |
| Submit weekly report | ✅ (own) | ✅ (own interns) | ❌ |
| View all users | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Approve supervisors | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Platform statistics | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |

