## File Uploads

- Files are stored in the `uploads/` directory
- Accessible at `http://localhost:5000/uploads/<filename>`
- Allowed types: PDF, DOC, DOCX, PNG, JPG, JPEG
- Max size: 5MB per file
- Reports support up to 5 attachments

